Goal must be clear,specific,defined.
SMART - Specific, Measureable, Achievable, Realistic and Time Bound.
GOAL should be there in all areas : Finance, Health, Relations, Envioronmental, Social.

steps to achieve goal:
1) Why 
2) Goals in front of you
3) Knowledge, skills and resources
4) Define Process Goals
5) Visualize
6) Find an Expert/Mentor/Coach
7) Never give up

Ask yourself every month about new learning
What one skill if I developed would help me the most to achieve my goals

without Process goal not possible to achieve end goal
